asset.hookText:
Victorinox was born in the village of Ibach in the heart of Switzerland, in a landscape of forests, mountains and lakes. Land of extraordinary legends filled with brave and enchanting heroes.
Victorinox Swiss Army is reviving, in its own inimitable way, three Swiss stories emblematic of this land's heritage. Follow the new adventures of these famous heroes, as they confront, with humour and resourcefulness, the unexpected realities of the modern world. 
Three myths, three stories, and three original short films, released over the course of the year.
In the first episode, you will meet a young girl, whose name will probably ring a bell, as she tries, by every means imaginable, to get her hands on her grandfather's watch ...
